@startuml
title aftersale-service 组件图 (Level 3)

skinparam componentStyle uml1

package "aftersale-service" {
  [AftersaleController] << Buyer API >>
  [AftersaleAdminController] << Admin API >>
  [AftersaleInternalApi] << Internal / Dubbo >>
  [WarehouseController] << 仓内 API >>

  [AftersaleService] << 核心服务 >>
  [AuditRuleEngine] << SpEL 规则引擎 >>
  [AftersaleStateMachine] << 售后状态机 >>
  [InspectionService] << 质检服务 >>

  [SagaClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [PaymentClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [OrderClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [InventoryClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [CouponClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [LogisticsClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [MemberClient] << Dubbo Client >>
  [NotificationClient] << MQ Producer >>

  [AftersaleReconJob] << XXL-Job >>

  database "MySQL\naftersale DB" as db {
    [aftersale_order]
    [inspection_record]
    [aftersale_sla_log]
  }

  database "Caffeine\nL1 Cache" as cache
}

' === 内部调用关系 ===
AftersaleController --> AftersaleService : 买家售后
AftersaleAdminController --> AftersaleService : 客服审核
WarehouseController --> InspectionService : 签收/质检
AftersaleController --> AuditRuleEngine : 审核判定（创建）

AftersaleService --> AftersaleStateMachine : 状态迁移校验
AftersaleService --> AuditRuleEngine : 审核规则匹配

InspectionService --> AftersaleService : 质检结果更新状态

AftersaleService --> SagaClient : 启动退款/换货 Saga
AftersaleService --> PaymentClient : 发起退款
AftersaleService --> OrderClient : 同步订单状态
AftersaleService --> InventoryClient : 释放/回滚库存
AftersaleService --> CouponClient : 回退优惠券
AftersaleService --> LogisticsClient : 退货物流查询/换货发货
AftersaleService --> MemberClient : 平台余额退款
AftersaleService --> NotificationClient : 售后通知

AftersaleService --> db : JPA / JDBC
AftersaleService --> cache : 查询缓存

AftersaleReconJob --> AftersaleService : 数据一致性对账

@enduml
